Athletics and Sports
lead_paragraph: Rutgers Coach C. Vivian Stringer benched her starting rotation Saturday, saying that she was not pleased by a loss to Duke earlier in the week. It didn’t stop her Scarlet Kings from rolling past Army, 59-42.
